The Commission of Inquiry into State Capture has adjourned until Monday when former BOSASA COO Antonio Agrizzi will take the stand again. On Thursday, a recording of a meeting between Agrizzi, BOSASA CEO Gavin Watson and former Correctional Services Commissioner Linda Mti in May 2015 was viewed. In the recording Watson said he wanted to speak to former President Jacob Zuma about the appointment of a new National Director of Public Prosecutions that would protect BOSASA from prosecution. Click on videos below    